'''Erased Tapes Records'''是一間2007年成立、以[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]為據點的獨立音樂廠牌，致力於發行前衛音樂。

==發展過程==
德國出生的Robert Raths於2007年在英國倫敦創立的音樂廠牌公司，首先發行了Ryan Lee West以Aparatec為名的EP《Vemeer》，Erased Tapes經常與FELD、Supermundane、以及Gregory Euclide設計師合作<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://gregoryeuclide.com/2013/05/performing/ |title=Performing |publisher=Gregory Euclide |date=2013-05-15 |accessdate=2015-11-30 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203927/http://gregoryeuclide.com/2013/05/performing/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因此以旗下唱片的獨特包裝設計視覺美學聞名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.clashmusic.com/feature/label-profile-erased-tapes |title=Label Profile: Erased Tapes | Features | Clash Magazine |website=Clashmusic.com |date=2015-10-21 |accessdate=2015-11-30 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923222613/http://www.clashmusic.com/feature/label-profile-erased-tapes |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Betts |first=Stephen |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/10-new-artists-you-need-to-know-april-2015-20150416/michael-price-20150415 |title=Michael Price Photo - Bully, Kehlani and 8 More New Artists You Need to Know |publisher=Rolling Stone |date=2015-04-15 |accessdate=2015-11-30 |archive-date=2016-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202131037/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/pictures/10-new-artists-you-need-to-know-april-2015-20150416/michael-price-20150415 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且每發行十張唱片後便會推出一張免費的音樂合輯<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.erasedtapes.com/about |title=Erased Tapes Records - About |website=Erasedtapes.com |date=2007-02-05 |accessdate=2015-11-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924001647/http://www.erasedtapes.com/about |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年成立出版事業部「Erased Tapes Music」。

